description:
This is a 2 minute workout called 'Granite State Challenge' from the channel Mike Dostal.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Competitor and The Firestarter vibe.
The The Competitor vibe means Gamified, leaderboard-driven, full-send energy. This is especially good for Those who need to chase a score or beat their own record. The The Firestarter vibe means Fast, explosive, and electrifying. Short but devastating. This is especially good for When you only have 10-20 minutes but want to give 1000%..
The technique difficulty is Advanced and Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging and Extreme.
